OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FThe leader of Wiltshire Council has
OL,7,Fclaimed the Government is "spiteful",
OL,8,F"nasty" and "kicking rural England",
OL,9,Fwhile describing Labour's plans for
OL,10,Fdevolution as unhelpful.
OL,12,FSpeaking on The West Country Debate,
OL,13,FConservative councillor Richard Clewer
OL,14,Fslammed the government's decision to
OL,15,Fscrap the rural services grant, which
OL,16,Fcomes as a result of proposed changes
OL,17,Fto local authority funding that would
OL,18,Fsee more cash given to deprived areas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
