OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FCllr Clewer, who has led Wiltshire
OL,7,FCouncil since 2021, also said he
OL,8,Fdisagrees with Labour's plans to
OL,9,Fintroduce elected mayors across the
OL,10,Fcountry, ahead of an English
OL,11,FDevolution White Paper due to be
OL,12,Fpublished next week.
OL,14,F"I personally dislike the idea of a
OL,15,Fmayor, I don't think it's helpful -
OL,16,Fbut that's what (the) Government has
OL,17,Fsaid", he said. "Ministers have been
OL,18,Fabsolutely clear that you've got to
OL,19,Fhave a mayor."
