OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FTessa Munt, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,7,Ffor Wells and Mendip Hills, added:
OL,8,F"When it is utterly clear that if you
OL,9,Fdo not have a mayor, you do not get
OL,10,Fthe money, it is pretty clear what
OL,11,Fsort of choice we all have to make.
OL,12,FThere's no choice attached to that."
OL,14,FThe three politicians also clashed
OL,15,Fover the prime minister's 'six
OL,16,Fmilestones' on The West Country Debate.
OL,18,FCllr Clewer said Sir Kier Starmer has
OL,19,Fset out a "good vision" but claimed
OL,20,FLabour was unable to deliver on it's
OL,21,Fpromises.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
