OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,F"The housing targets that they are
OL,7,Fcoming up with are based on arbitrary
OL,8,Fnumbers and they're piling a lot more
OL,9,Fhouses into rural areas", he said.
OL,11,F"We've just seen the revised (National
OL,12,FPlanning Policy Framework) today -
OL,13,Fit's putting in even more houses. It's
OL,14,Ftaking from the North, putting it into
OL,15,Fnon-Labour areas from the South.
OL,16,FThere's a vindictiveness there that
OL,17,Fisn't helpful. And then on top of
OL,18,Fthat, you've got a viability and a
OL,19,Fdeliverability issue."
