OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Ms Munt warned the crisis
OL,7,Fin funding for special educational
OL,8,Fneeds and disabilities "will bring
OL,9,Fcouncils down".
OL,11,F"The previous government was silly
OL,12,Fenough to actually just go la-la-la-la-
OL,13,Fla-la, and say 'you can shove this
OL,14,Fdeficit... you can ignore it, pretend
OL,15,Fit doesn't exist", she added.
OL,17,FBut Cllr Clewer said the previous
OL,18,FConservative government "wasn't
OL,19,Fignoring it".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
