OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FHe added: "There were some well
OL,7,Fintentioned changes that were brought
OL,8,Fthrough in, in what, 2014 that have
OL,9,Fhad a serious knock-on impact. The
OL,10,FGovernment had started to take steps
OL,11,Fthrough what was called the Safety
OL,12,FValve Programme."
OL,14,FCllr Clewer added the problem of
OL,15,Fcouncil's being made to spend more
OL,16,Fthan they can afford on SEND only
OL,17,F"became apparent" about four years ago
OL,18,F- something Ms Munt disagreed with.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
