OL,3,CCouncil leader warns Labour is
OL,4,C'kicking rural England'
OL,6,FCamborne and Redruth's MP, Mr Moon,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've got investment going into
OL,8,Fschools, investment going into the
OL,9,FNHS. When I go and visit local
OL,10,Fbusinesses in my constituency, it is
OL,11,Fschools, it is housing, it is the NHS
OL,12,Fthat they want to see fixed, and they
OL,13,Fare Labour's priorities."
OL,15,FYou can watch the full edition of The
OL,16,FWest Country Debate on ITV1 on
OL,17,FThursday 12 December at 10:45 and on
OL,18,FITVX.
